        {
            "id": 6076714,
            "title": "谷歌 引爆AI軍備競賽快速升級！CCL、PCB、CPO 火線爆發！上半年就大增60%，下半年才真正量產出貨是？",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>投資朋友問：昨日美股有何關注的重點呢？</strong></p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6076714/l/8d0bbe9c29929fee994dbff908b45ea2.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">谷歌 引爆AI軍備競賽快速升級！CCL、PCB、CPO 火線爆發！上半年就大增60%，下半年才真正量產出貨是？ (圖:shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>特斯拉 (</strong><a href=\"https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E7%89%B9%E6%96%AF%E6%8B%89%E8%B2%A1%E5%A0%B1%E6%85%98%E6%B7%A1-%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E5%B9%BE%E5%AD%A3%E6%9C%83%E5%BE%88%E8%89%B1%E9%9B%A3-012740264.html\"><strong>TSLA-US</strong></a><strong>)</strong><strong> 公布財報，並因電動車激勵措施到期，預計未來幾季將會很艱難，股價大跌 8.2%。而 Alphabet (</strong><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GOOGL\" target=\"_self\"><strong>GOOGL-US</strong></a><strong>)</strong><strong> 受惠於 AI 需求，全年資本支出預期從 750 億美元上調至 850 億美元。從 Alphabet 上調資本支出的動作，AI 軍備競賽持續升級中。</strong></p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>葉俊敏分析師表示，市場資金持續看好成長快速的 AI 產業，轉型 AI 較慢的蘋果 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AAPL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AAPL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AAPL-US</a>) 今年跌逾 12%。而輝達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>)今年漲逾 25%</strong><strong>；</strong><strong>AMD(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMD-US</a>)</strong><strong> 今年漲逾 34%</strong><strong>；</strong><strong>微軟 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MSFT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MSFT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MSFT-US</a>) 今年漲逾 22%；Meta (</strong><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/META\" target=\"_self\"><strong>META-US</strong></a><strong>) </strong><strong>今年漲逾 19% 。在 FANG + 股中，蘋果是今年唯一下跌的個股，所以投資朋友還是要關注 AI 產業鏈。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>投資朋友問：國防部軍備局公告採購無人機後，相關供應鏈出現大漲，該如何看待無人機產業呢？</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>葉俊敏分析師表示，烏俄衝突以來，無人機在戰場上展現價值，也讓各國因國防安全開始建立本土供應鏈。全球軍用無人機市場迎來大成長，Fortune Business Insights 報告預測，全球軍用無人機市場規模預計從 2024 年的 160.7 億美元成長至 2032 年達到 471.6 億美元，年複合成長率為 13.15%。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>2024</strong><strong> 年美國公告國防授權法案 (NDAA) 及「美國安全無人機法案」，以求建立無人機的本土供應鏈，美國無人機股 AeroVironment(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AVAV:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AVAV\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AVAV-US</a>)今年累計漲幅逾 70%。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>國防部軍備局於 (7/22) 公告，預計於 2026 至 2027 年籌獲甲、乙、丙、丁、戊共 5 款軍用商規無人機，涵蓋短中長程與不同可酬載重量，起降類型分：多軸旋翼機、定翼機彈射與垂直起降型等，共 4 萬 8750 架，市場規模預估上看 500 億元，29 日舉行將徵商說明會。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>從以上資料來看，不管從國際與台灣的角度來看，無人機產業都將有高成長，投資朋友可以留意其中具有關鍵技術的供應鏈布局。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>葉俊敏分析師提供，AI 產業鏈與無人機供應鏈，給投資朋友參考－</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>玻纖布：台玻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1802:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1802\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1802-TW</a>)、富喬 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1815:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1815\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1815-TW</a>)、德宏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5475:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5475\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5475-TW</a>)</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>PCB</strong><strong>：高技 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5439:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5439\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5439-TW</a>)、精成科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6191:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6191\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6191-TW</a>)、金像電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2368:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2368\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2368-TW</a>)、定穎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3715:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3715\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3715-TW</a>)</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>CCL</strong><strong>：台光電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2383:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2383\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2383-TW</a>)、台燿 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6274:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6274\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6274-TW</a>)、聯茂 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6213:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6213\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6213-TW</a>)</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>CPO</strong><strong>：環宇 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4991:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4991\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4991-TW</a>)、IET-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4971:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4971\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4971-TW</a>)、上詮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3363:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3363\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3363-TW</a>)、波若威 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3163:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3163\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3163-TW</a>)、聯鈞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3450:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3450\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3450-TW</a>)、華星光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4979:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4979\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4979-TW</a>)、訊芯 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6451:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6451\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6451-TW</a>)、眾達 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4977:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4977\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4977-TW</a>)、光聖 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6442:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6442\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6442-TW</a>)、聯亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3081:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3081\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3081-TW</a>)</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>無人機：雷虎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8033:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data